<pb ed="T" id="T17.0808.0754a" n="0754a"/>
<lb n="0754a01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0754a02"/><head>No. 808 [No. 809]</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0754a03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title>佛說犢子經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0754a04"/>
<lb n="0754a05"/><byline type="Translator">吳月<note n="0754001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">氏＝支【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">氏＝支【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754001"><lem>氏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">支</rdg></app>優婆塞支謙<note n="0754002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（初）＋譯【元】【明】</note><app n="0754002"><lem>譯</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">初譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0754a06"/><p>聞如是。一時佛在舍衛國祇<note n="0754003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">洹＝桓【三】【聖】</note><note n="0754003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">洹＝桓【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0754003"><lem>洹</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">桓</rdg></app>阿那邠遲阿
<lb n="0754a07"/>藍精舍。爾時佛<note n="0754004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遇風患＝患風【宮】</note><app n="0754004"><lem>遇風患</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">患風</rdg></app>當須牛乳。時有婆羅
<lb n="0754a08"/>門大富去城不遠。時佛遣阿難言。汝往到婆
<lb n="0754a09"/>羅門家從乞牛乳。阿難受教而往。<note n="0754005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔便〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔便〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754005"><lem>便</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0754006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">至＝到【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">至＝到【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754006"><lem>至</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">到</rdg></app>婆
<lb n="0754a10"/>羅門家。婆羅門問阿難<note n="0754007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔言〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔言〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754007"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。來何所求。阿難
<lb n="0754a11"/>言。如來向者少遇風患。<note n="0754008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">故遣我＝使我來【三】，故使我來【宮】</note><note n="0754008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">故遣我＝使我來【宋】【元】【明】，＝故使我來【宮】</note><app n="0754008"><lem>故遣我</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">使我來</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">故使我來</rdg></app>乞牛乳耳。
<lb n="0754a12"/>婆羅門言。牛在彼間自&CB00590;取之。阿難即往到
<lb n="0754a13"/>牛<note n="0754009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔群〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔群〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754009"><lem>群</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>所。<note n="0754010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔有一〕－【三】，有一牸牛性常＝牛當【宮】</note><note n="0754010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有一牸牛性常＝牛當【宮】，〔有一〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0754010"><lem>有一牸牛。性常</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">牛當</rdg><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">牸牛性常</rdg></app>弊惡無人能近。阿
<lb n="0754a14"/>難即自思惟。我法不應自&CB00590;取牛乳</p>
<lb n="0754a15"/><p>爾時帝釋知阿難所念。即來化作婆羅門像
<lb n="0754a16"/>在牛邊立。阿難往倩言。婆羅門為我&CB00590;取牛
<lb n="0754a17"/><note n="0754011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乳＋（婆羅門言諾即前以右手捫摸牛乳）【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0754011" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>乳＋（婆羅門言諾即前以右手捫摸牛乳）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0754011"><lem>乳</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">乳婆羅門言諾即前以右手捫摸牛乳</rdg></app>。語牛言。如來遇小風患。汝與乳<note n="0754012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">湩＝&CB05630;【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">湩＝&CB05630;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754012"><lem>湩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&CB05630;</rdg></app>令如
<lb n="0754a18"/>來服之。差者汝得福無量不可稱計。如來者
<lb n="0754a19"/>是天上天下之大師也。<note n="0754013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＝常【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當＝常【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754013"><lem>當</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">常</rdg></app>以慈心憂念一切
<lb n="0754a20"/>蠕動之類。欲令度脫一切苦惱。牛言。此手捫
<lb n="0754a21"/>摸我乳。一何快耶。前兩乳取去。置後兩乳用
<lb n="0754a22"/>遺我子。我子朝來未有所食</p>
<lb n="0754a23"/><p>爾時犢子在邊立住。聞有佛名即語母言。持
<lb n="0754a24"/>我乳分盡用與佛。佛<note n="0754014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者＋（是）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者＋（是）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754014"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">者是</rdg></app>天上天下之大師也。
<lb n="0754a25"/>甚難得值。我自食草飲水足得活耳。何以故。
<lb n="0754a26"/>我先身以來常飲乳食。今<note n="0754015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＝作畜【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當＝作畜【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754015"><lem>當</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">作畜</rdg></app>生牛身亦復飲
<lb n="0754a27"/>乳。世間愚癡者甚多無量。我先世時坐隨惡
<lb n="0754a28"/>知識教不信佛經。使我作牛作馬經十六劫。
<lb n="0754a29"/>而今乃得聞有佛名。持我所<note n="0754016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食＋（乳）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食＋（乳）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754016"><lem>食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">食乳</rdg></app>分盡用與佛
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0808.0754b" n="0754b"/>
<lb n="0754b01"/>滿器而去。令我後世智慧聰明得道如佛。阿
<lb n="0754b02"/>難持乳還至佛所</p>
<lb n="0754b03"/><p>佛問阿難。彼牛母子有何言說。阿難言。大可
<lb n="0754b04"/>怪也。牛先甚<note n="0754017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔大〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754017"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>弊惡不可得近。有一婆羅門
<lb n="0754b05"/>為我&CB00590;乳。牛即調善。<note n="0754018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">母子＝子母【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">母子＝子母【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754018"><lem>母子</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">子母</rdg></app>共說。佛言。此牛
<lb n="0754b06"/>子母。先<note n="0754019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世＋（之）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世＋（之）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754019"><lem>世</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">世之</rdg></app>時不信佛經故。墮牛馬中經十六
<lb n="0754b07"/>劫。今乃得悟聞有佛<note n="0754020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔名〕－【宋】【元】，明註曰南藏無名字</note><app n="0754020"><lem>名</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【南藏】" resp="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>。<note n="0754021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＝使【宮】</note><app n="0754021"><lem>便</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">使</rdg></app><note n="0754022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔有〕－【宮】</note><app n="0754022"><lem>有</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0754023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（我）＋慈【三】</note><note n="0754023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（我）＋慈【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0754023"><lem>慈</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">我慈</rdg></app>心以乳
<lb n="0754b08"/>施佛。彼牛母子。後<note n="0754024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世＝身【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世＝身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754024"><lem>世</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">身</rdg></app>當為彌勒佛<note n="0754025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（作）＋沙門【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（作）＋沙門【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754025"><lem>沙門</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">作沙門</rdg></app>弟
<lb n="0754b09"/>子得大羅漢。犢子死後當為我懸繒幡蓋。散
<lb n="0754b10"/>華燒香受持經戒。過二十劫後當作佛。名乳
<lb n="0754b11"/>光如來度脫一切。佛言。牛以好<note n="0754026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善心＝心善【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善心＝心善【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754026"><lem>善心</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">心善</rdg></app>意與佛
<lb n="0754b12"/>乳故。度諸苦難。<note n="0754027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔後〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔後〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754027"><lem>後</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>得無量福報。以是因緣。
<lb n="0754b13"/>佛不可不<note n="0754028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">信＝事【三】【宮】</note><note n="0754028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">信＝事【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0754028"><lem>信</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">事</rdg></app>。經不可不讀。道不可不學。普
<lb n="0754b14"/>告天上天下皆悉令知</p>
<lb n="0754b15"/><trailer><title>佛說犢子經</title></trailer><juan fun="close" n="001"></juan></div1>
